Si kastaba ha ahaatee, neefsashada iyo neefsashada la'aanta ayaa ah khatarta ugu weyn ee cudurka iyo sababta ugu weyn ee dhimashada.
Sidaa darteed, taageerada neefsashada waa muhiim si loo yareeyo astaamaha cudurka iyo badbaadada nolosha waxayna ka kooban tahay dhammaan daaweynta hawada, hawada dhaqdhaqaaqa, helitaanka hawada ka timaadda qalabka, waxay kuxirantahay heerka cudurka.
Bukaanka qaba cudurka neefsashada ee daran waa in lagu taageertaa ECMO, oo ah farsamo kale oo wadnaha lagu isticmaalo daaweynta cudurrada wadnaha ee halista ah ama fashilka neefsashada.
Intaa waxaa dheer, hagaajinta heerarka elektrolyte, ka hortagga iyo daaweynta cudurka iyo ka hortagga jirka, iyo ka hortagga howlaha xubnaha jirka ayaa sidoo kale muhiim u ah bukaannada SARS-CoV-2.
Cudurka cytokine-ka ayaa loo yaqaanaa inuu ka dhalanayo nidaamka difaaca jirka ee ka badan inta lagu jiro bukaanka SARS iyo MERS.
Cytokine-ka dabaysha waa nooc ka mid ah falcelinta nidaamka caabuqa ee dabaysha ee lagu soo bandhigo taxane cytokines ah oo ay ku jiraan TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, iyo MCP-1.
Cytokines-yadaas oo leh unugyo difaaca ayaa sii deynaya tiro badan oo ka mid ah unugyada aan la beddeli karin ee ah sababaha ugu waaweyn ee ARDS iyo cillad badan oo xubnaha jirka ah.
Dhibicda tallaalka waa mid muhiim u ah in la ogaado sida ay u kordhayaan cytokines, gaar ahaan dadka da'da ah ee aad u nugul.
Corticosteroids iyo tocilizumab, oo ah difaaca anti-IL6 monoclonal, ayaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu daaweeyo dabaysha cytokine.
Daaweynta kale ee tallaalka ee ku saabsan cudurka cytokine waxaa ka mid ah hagaajinta iyo jawaab celinta tooska ah ee unugyada T ee ka hortagga cudurka; IFN-γ, IL-1, iyo TNF-ka; JAK inhibitor; blinatumomab; cytokine inhibitor; iyo HDAC inhibitors.
Daawooyinka Steroids, sida immunosuppressants, ayaa si weyn loogu isticmaalay daaweynta SARS si loo yareeyo waxyeelada daran ee caabuqa.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, qaadashada steroids-ka xad dhaafka ah ma faa'iideysato dhaawaca sanbabada ee daran ee bukaannada SARS iyo COVID-19.
Taa bedelkeeda, waxay keeni karaan waxyeelo daran, gaar ahaan cudurrada osteonecrosis, taas oo keentay saameynta cudurka.
