Cilmi-baarista horumarsan ee ku saabsan aagga ayaa u oggolaan doonta habka horumarinta SARS-CoV-2 ee xayawaanka, iyadoo saameyn muhiim ah ku yeelan doonta ka hortagga iyo xakamaynta COVID-19 ee aadanaha.
Xeerarka baaritaanka COVID-19 oo loo maleynayo inay ku dhaceen iyo oo horay loo ogaaday inay qabaan  ayaa la cusbooneysiiyay
6 Febraayo 2020, kooxdeena waxay daabacday hage tallaabo deg deg ah oo lagu ogaado iyo la socodsiinta cudurka 2019 noro coronavirus (2019-nCoV), hagegaan ayaa na siinaya khibradeena iyo fikrado badan oo ku saabsan la dagaalanka cudurkan caalamiga ah.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, cudurka faafa ee coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) waa cudur cusub, wacyiga iyo aqoonta ayaa si tartiib tartiib ah u sii kordheysa iyadoo lagu saleynayo cilmi baarista horumarsan iyo khibradda caafimaadka; Sidaa darteed, farsamooyinka cudurka iyo daaweynta ayaa sidoo kale si joogto ah loo cusbooneysiiyay.
Warqaddan, waxaan ka jawaabnay hal jawaab oo ku saabsan tilmaamaheena waxaanan soo saarnay xaalad cusub oo cilmi baaris ah oo loogu talagalay ka shakiga ah ka cudurka ka cudurka ka xaqiiqda ah  sida ku cad cilmi baarista ugu dambeysay ee COVID-19 (daabacaadda toddobaad) ee ay soo saartay Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Jamhuuriyadda Dadka Shiinaha.
Bishii Diseembar 2019, coronavirus-ka sanadka 2019 (2019-nCoV) ayaa sababay faafitaan, oo hadda loo magacaabay coronavirus-ka 2019 (COVID-19) waxaana loo magacaabay fayraska kuleylka culus ee coronavirus-ka 2 (SARS-CoV- 2).
Bishii Maarso 11, 2020, WHO waxay COVID-19 ku tilmaantay cudur faafa.
Si looga hortago cudurrada faafa ee SARS-CoV-2, kooxdeena waxay soo saartay hagitaan degdeg ah oo lagu daabacay khadka tooska ah ee Warbixinta Caafimaadka Ciidamada ee 06 Febraayo 2020.
Tan iyo markii la daabacay, waxaa la soo jiitay dareen aad u weyn.
Ogsoonow in inkastoo COVID-19 uu yahay cudur cusub, aqoonta iyo aqoonta aan ku leenahay ay si tartiib tartiib ah u kordhayaan iyadoo lagu saleynayo cilmi baarista horumarsan iyo khibradda caafimaadka; sidaa darteed, farsamooyinka cudur-saarka iyo daaweynta ayaa sidoo kale si joogto ah loo cusbooneysiiyaa.
Tusaale ahaan, Daraasadda Cilmi-baarista iyo Tilmaamaha Daaweynta ee COVID-19 ee ay soo saartay Guddiga Caafimaadka ee Jamhuuriyadda Dadka ee Shiinaha (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), intii u dhaxaysay 16 Janaayo 2020 ilaa 3 Maarso 2020, waxay soo saartay wadar ahaan toddoba daabac oo ay weheliso qaar ka mid ah mawduucyada isbedelka weyn.
