Si kastaba ha noqotee, shaqadooda ayaa sidoo kale u baahan in la cusbooneysiiyo iyadoo la raacayo Caddaynta Asalka iyo Tilmaamaha Caafimaadka COVID-19 (Testillada Toddoba) iyo daraasadaha dhowaan.
Sida laga soo xigtay daabacaadda toddobaad (3 Maarso 2020), si loo xaqiijiyo eedeymaha loo baahan yahay in la isku daro hal shay oo ka mid ah taariikhda cudurka faafa oo leh laba shay oo muujinaya astaamaha bukaanka si loo sameeyo baaritaan dhammaystiran, ama loo baahan yahay in la isku daro saddex shay oo muujinaya astaamaha bukaanka haddii aan la helin taariikhda cudurka faafa oo cad:
Taariikhda cudurrada: (1) taariikhda safarka ama deganaanshaha magaalada Wuhan iyo agagaarka, ama bulshooyinka kale ee laga soo sheegay COVID-19 14kii maalmood ee ugu dambeeyay ka hor calaamadaha bilowga; (2) taariikhda la xiriirka cudurka SARS-CoV-2 ee maqaarka (oo leh baaritaan ku habboon oo nucleic acid);(3) taariikhda la xiriirka bukaannada qaba hargab ama calaamadaha neefsashada ka yimid magaalada Wuhan iyo agagaarka, ama bulshooyinka kale ee laga soo sheegay COVID-19 14kii maalmood ee ugu dambeeyay ka hor calaamadaha bilowga;(≥4) taariikhda la xiriirka isku-darka dhacdooyinka la xaqiijiyay (((≥ 2 jeer oo hargabka iyo / ama calaamadaha cudurka neefsashada ayaa ka dhacay 2 toddobaad gudahood meelo yar oo heerkul ah, sida guriga, xafiiska, dugsiga, iwm.).
Muuqaalka cudurrada caafimaad: (1) hargabka iyo/ama calaamadaha cudurka neefsashada; (2) calaamadaha farsamada ee cudurka COVID-19; (3) tirada unugyada dhiigga cad ee muujinaya saxda ah, hoos u dhac, ama hoos u dhac ku yimid tirada lymphocyte ee barta koowaad.
Baaritaanka kiiska la xaqiijiyay waa inuu ku saleysan yahay eedeymaha la sheegay in ay la socdaan hal shay oo cudur-darrada ah ama caddayn serological ah sida soo socota: (1) baaritaanka PCR ee run ahaantii ah ee SARS-CoV-2; (2) sawir ama fiidiyow degdeg ah oo ku saabsan dhammaan nidaamyada dabiiciga ah ee muujinaya dabeecad sare oo loogu talagalay coronaviruses-yada la yaqaan; (3) mid ku habboon IgM antibody iyo IgG antibody gaar ah ee SARS-CoV-2 baaritaanka serum; ama bedelka SARG-CoV-2-IgG ee IgG gaar ah oo ka soo baxa mid xun oo wanaagsan, ama titer ≥4 jeer inta lagu jiro waqtiga soo kabashada ee ugu adag ee waqtiga.
Waxaan arki karnaa in tijaabada PCR ee saxda ah ee nucleic acid ee nidaamka neefsashada ama muunadaha dhiigga ay kordheen labaad (18 Janaayo 2020) iyo saddexaad (22 Janaayo 2020).
Xogta dhiigga ee la soo saaray ayaa lagu ogaaday daabacaadda afraad (27 Janaayo 2020) iyo shanaad (8 Febraayo 2020); ka dibna caddaynta serological ayaa lagu daray daabacaadda toddobaad.
