Qalabka gacmaha lagu nadiifiyo ama saliidda ka hortagga fayraska oo asal ahaan ka soo jeeda nadaafadda gacmaha aan biyo lahayn.
Dhamaadkii 1990-meeyadii iyo bilowgii qarnigii 21-aad, waxyaabaha gacmaha lagu nadiifiyo ee khamriga iyo biyaha la'aanta ah (oo sidoo kale loo yaqaan saliidda gacmaha ee khamriga leh, saliidda gacmaha ee daawooyinka, ama saliidda gacmaha lagu nadiifiyo) ayaa caan ku noqday.
Inta badan waxay ku tiirsan yihiin isopropyl alcohol ama ethanol oo lagu daro walxaha ay u adkeystaan sida Carbomer (polymer acrylic acid) saliid, ama hemectant sida glycerin biyaha, ama kumbuyuutar si fudud loo isticmaalo ka dibna loo yareeyo saameynta qalajinta ee khamriga.
