Dhammaan alaabada waa in la ilaaliyaa saddexda tallaabo ee badbaadada dabiiciga ah ee loo yaqaan 'Biosafety Level 3 precautions'.
Hay'adda Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) waxay soo jeedisay in bukaannada cusub ee ku jira meelo kala duwan ay ku kala saaraan qaraabada ama qof kale oo ku dhacay COVID-19. Marka lagu daro PPE-yada qaarkood, OSHA waxay soo jeedineysaa in loo isticmaalo qalabka neefsashada dadka ka shaqeeya inta u dhaxaysa 6 jir oo la ogaaday ama laga helay cudurka, SARS-COV-2, iyo kuwa ku dhaqma nidaamka buufinta aerosol-generating procedures.
Maraykanka, NIOSH waxay ansixisay N95 si loo shaandheeyo qalabka neefsashada ama xitaa loo isticmaalo si sax ah, waxaa la helay ilaalinta ay ku jiraan baaritaan wanaagsan, waxbarasho iyo tijaabooyin caafimaad.
