BAngiotensin enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xiran dusha sare (celluunka unugyada) ee unugyada sanbabada, xididdada, wadnaha, kelyaha, iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay qiimeysaa waxqabadka enzyme-ka isku xirka (ACE) iyada oo la yareeyo heerarka angiotensin-II iyo kordhinta Ang (1-7) taas oo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed muhiim u ah daaweynta cudurrada wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa sidii waddo u galaan unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronaviruses.
Xakamaynta enzymes ee aadanaha waxaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Enzyme-ka ugu muhiimsan ee Angiotensin 2 waa zinc oo ku jira ironloenzyme oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada kale ee endothelial.
ACE2 waxay ka kooban tahay qayb ka mid ah N-terminal peptidase M2 iyo qayb ka mid ah C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transportar domain.
ACE2 waa nooc ka mid ah borotiinka gudbinta, oo leh qayb enzymatically firfircoon oo soo bandhigaysa heerka unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale ee jirka.
Meelaha ka baxsan unugyada ee ACE2 waxaa laga soo saaray meel bakteeri ah oo ay ku jirto enzyme loo yaqaan 'blood-leakage', waxaana natiijada ka dibna borotiinka dhalaalaya lagu soo saaraa dhiigga oo ugu dambeyntii lagu sii daayaa cirbadaha.
ACE2 waxaa laga helaa xubno badan: ACE2 waxay isku dartaa maqaarka ugu badan ee unugyada dufanka ee nooca II ee unugyada alveolar, enterocytes-ka mindhicirka, unugyada neerfaha iyo unugyada neerfaha ee unugyada wadnaha iyo unugyada muruqyada jilicsan ee unugyada badankood.
ACE2 MRNA-yada dambe waxaa laga heli karaa maskaxda maskaxda, hypotamalamus-ka iyo briainstem-ka.
Shaqada koowaad ee ACE2 waa inay u istaagto inay tahay qiyaasta isku dheelitirka ee ACE.
ACE waxay ku dhejisaa angiotensin I hormone ee angiotensin II vasoconstricting.
ACE2 ayaa si isdaba joog ah u soo saarta carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine oo ka soo jeeda angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) waxayna u hydrolyses in angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay baabi'in kartaa peptides kale oo ay ku jiraan [des-Arg9] -bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale hagaajineysaa wareegga xajmiga ee dhexdhexaadiyaha amino acid SLC6A19 waxayna la xiriirtaa cudurka Hartnup.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 waxay u shaqeysaa sidii xakamaynta ugu weyn ee unugyada (Cell) ee qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-yada, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (viruska sababa SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska sababa COVID-19).
Xayawaanka sida isku darka borotiinka spike s1 ee sars-cov iyo sars-cov2 waxay ku darsadaan bukaanka ACE2 ee xarunta unugyada taas oo si fudud u horseedaysa endocytosis iyo wareejinta cudurka iyo xitaa unugyada xayawaanka ee ku jira endosome ee unugyada.
Xiriirka tar-ka oo leh dhammaan shuruudaha priming ee borotiinka S wuxuu ka yimid serine protease TMPRSS2, iyo sameynta midka loo baaro in uu yahay mid aad u weyn oo loo yaqaan 'thrapeutic'. taas oo horseeday hoos u dhac ku yimaada heerka ACE2, unugyada, taas oo ka caawin karta in la dagaalamo cudurka.
Inkastoo ay badan yihiin dadka qaba cayayaanka ayaa u baahan horumarinta nidaamka ACE inhibitor ee ARB therapy.
